Package: bendr
Type: Package
Title: Nested Dirichlet Process Mixture Models for Built Environment Data
Version: 1.0.4
Date: 2020-10-16
Authors@R: person(given = "Adam", 
				  family = "Peterson", 
				  email ="atpvyc@umich.edu", 
				  role = c("aut", "cre"),
				  comment = c(ORCID = 0000-0001-7071-7873))
Description: Motivated by the need to identify different kinds of built environments,
  the bendr package estimates the spatial intensity function for different clusters
  of Inhomogenous Poisson Processes.
